+ Control Data\nExtraction Behavior
++ Extraction Patterns
+++_ Snapshot (full reload)
+++_ Incremental (CDC-based)
++ Change Data Capture
+++_ Gateway tracks inserts/updates/deletes
+++_ Only changed records processed
+++_ Requires CDC enabled on source
-- SCD Types
---_ SCD Type 1: overwrite current state
---_ SCD Type 2: preserve history
---_ __START_AT / __END_AT columns (SCD2)
-- Full Refresh
---_ Clears & reloads destination
---_ Minimize downtime (swap on completion)
---_ Schedule via full refresh window
@endmindmap
